item.title: Stunning image of Jupiter from NASA's Juno spacecraft is simply out of this world — except it's not
item.description: <img src="/img/2017/05/pia21390.jpeg" alt=""> <img src="/img/2017/05/pia21030-300x300.jpg" alt=""> The filagree of atmospheric patterns at Jupiter’s south pole bears an eerie resemblance to a phenomenon here on Earth Source: This stunning image of Jupiter from NASA&rsquo;s Juno spacecraft is simply out of this world — except it&rsquo;s not
